  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time candlestick charts for BTC, ETH, ADA, XRP, DOT, UNI via Binance WebSocket streams",
    "On-device processing — no cloud hosting, all data stays local",
    "React frontend embedded in a native desktop window via webview",
    "C++ backend with IXWebSocket for low-latency market data ingestion",
    "Switchable watchlist for selecting which coin to track",
    "Live price display updated on every market tick",
    "Cross-platform build system using CMake with vcpkg on Windows"
  ],
